lyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"佢只會痛 唔會停止到佢既動作 姐係無用"},{"pid":"be0f4dffe6c6c6928a81b2dce59b1c1bdcb614b6","tid":1350314,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc56e373d5b2f0adc1151102514475407109a5d0","tid":1350314,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cce705a0275a99cd3d515ba2199ecbb93cef71","tid":1350314,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13eb1a003ce906bef72669f9b67a13609a6e638","tid":1350314,"uid":92340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"講真，玩椏叉/射箭都勁過你氣槍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e476ee9cabbeb80a1b10480e6b1527de7cb0fb47","tid":1350314,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEKe9hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEKe9hf.jpg&h=7a953ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nco2 powered, 真槍運作模式<br />\n本身粒彈可以入十幾粒bb彈都可以打爆個膠桶， 但粒彈都可以入釘又得入螺絲又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b9a573a4d2a97e194dc6628c62718954cc616e","tid":1350314,"uid":225299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"2焦 唔會入肉 只會紅 隔日會瘀 <br />\n<br />\n氣槍係彷真槍 重量都幾重 十幾飛子彈你做唔到啲乜<br />\n行動都唔方便<br />\n<br />\n電槍 可以百幾粒咁比你掃 不過室外咁多人好易誤擊<br />\n<br />\n同埋兩種槍都係 當你1.7焦 你唔會每一發都係1.7焦<br />\n或以上 只會遞減<br />\n<br />\n另外極度唔建議帶槍出街自衛呢個方法<br />\n<br />\n利伸：game友 室外cqb都有玩，大前排有人攞槍亂<br />\n射街既人 咁岩撞正個排有game打要帶gear出去玩，正值敏感時期 所以都擔心，有上網搵資料 有啲咩後果，都幾大獲，同埋你咁樣做係會比狗個邊有藉口升級個武力 請三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144902f9a0a744738ebc170b1356c290b87b334c","tid":1350314,"uid":124958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"槍械牌照<br />\n<br />\n香港法例第238章《火器及彈藥條例》(&ldquo;條例&rdquo;)授權警務處處長向合適人士簽發槍械或彈藥的管有權牌照(&ldquo;牌照&rdquo;)，讓其合法管有槍械或彈藥。條例訂明任何可發射子彈或投射物，而槍口能量超過2焦耳的氣槍 (包括長槍型氣槍、氣槍或手槍型氣槍) 均屬槍械。<br />\n<br />\n唔多過2焦耳ok"},{"pid":"d60f83ac44081606c31fa8f1e60a1283f40e2f84","tid":1350314,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"對面有甲<br />\n除非無買真槍件玩鋼珠<br />\n如果唔係既話用丫差無咁嬲"},{"pid":"fec2f6b55b4a304d7fcb4959124c66e44eaa6129","tid":1350314,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15de12f6b0ab0ea73858c7b635f02ac81ae7bd9a","tid":1350314,"uid":161328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc56e373d5b2f0adc1151102514475407109a5d0","tid":1350314,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"40mm grenade 你打過game 就知得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43956096ac2783ccc73b75935a8d2a39d0757f14","tid":1350314,"uid":12182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"打開 但老實講唔會痛 應該冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n但如果大量bb彈/鋼珠係地下既話就好易仆街"},{"pid":"2456f2f2b872975010d32ba028e1b42b0d51f776","tid":1350314,"uid":161328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec2f6b55b4a304d7fcb4959124c66e44eaa6129","tid":1350314,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15de12f6b0ab0ea73858c7b635f02ac81ae7bd9a","tid":1350314,"uid":161328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc56e373d5b2f0adc1151102514475407109a5d0","tid":1350314,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim